            "type": "code",
            "language": "text",
            "code": ">>> x = np.array([1e-6, 4e-7, 2, 3])\n>>> np.array_repr(x, precision=6, suppress_small=True)\n'array([0.000001,  0.      ,  2.      ,  3.      ])'"
          }
